WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:05.088
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:05.088 --> 00:08.058
I'll tell you, Woody,
the psychiatric profession

00:08.058 --> 00:10.427
can really get rough sometimes.

00:10.427 --> 00:13.229
I think if I hear one
more person telling me

00:13.229 --> 00:14.731
about one more problem, I'll explode.

00:14.731 --> 00:17.100
I know just how you feel, Dr. Crane.

00:17.100 --> 00:18.351
Actually, I suppose you do.

00:18.351 --> 00:20.353
Our professions are
really very much alike.

00:20.353 --> 00:22.355
We both have to listen patiently

00:22.355 --> 00:24.824
while people unload
their grief and suffering.

00:24.824 --> 00:27.327
Sometimes it's just
more than I can bear.

00:27.327 --> 00:29.245
I know just how you feel, Dr. Crane.

00:29.245 --> 00:31.698
You know, if only I had
your ability to listen

00:31.698 --> 00:34.200
to a person's problem,
sympathize with them,

00:34.200 --> 00:37.203
and yet still go on about my
business calmly and happily.

00:37.203 --> 00:39.089
How do you do it, Wood?

00:39.089 --> 00:41.424
I know just how you feel, Dr. Crane.

00:43.376 --> 00:45.762
You're not listening to me, are you?

00:45.762 --> 00:47.964
I know just how you feel, Dr. Crane.

00:47.964 --> 00:50.133
How about a double scotch rocks?

00:50.133 --> 00:50.884
Coming right up.

00:53.386 --> 00:56.806
(piano plays)

00:56.806 --> 00:59.692
? Making your way in the world today ?

00:59.692 --> 01:02.695
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:02.695 --> 01:05.197
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:05.197 --> 01:08.701
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:08.701 --> 01:13.957
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:13.957 --> 01:16.743
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:16.743 --> 01:21.748
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:21.748 --> 01:26.753
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:26.753 --> 01:29.255
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:29.255 --> 01:31.758
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:31.758 --> 01:37.263
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:37.263 --> 01:39.766
? You want to go where people know ?

01:39.766 --> 01:41.768
? People are all the same ?

01:42.268 --> 01:46.272
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

